            <h3 class="title is-size-4 is-bold">Finding candidates for placement on permanent contracts</h3>
            <p class="text is-size-2">Akela Consulting combines traditional methods and online research to find candidates to suit any job vacancy. The agency works by participating in trade fairs, approaching directly potential candidates, advertising on professional social networks (Linkedln, Viadeo, etc) and on employment sites (Indeed, Monster, MétéoJob and others).</p>
